  <brief_title>Immune Benefits of Consumption of Dairy Yogurt in Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>Immune Benefits of Consumption of Dairy Yogurt Containing Functional Probiotics Among Individuals Over 60 Years Old</official_title>
  <sponsors>
